### ===========================================
### Career-Copilot API 测试
### 支持两种测试方式：
###
### 方式一：REST Client（本文件）
###   - 安装 VS Code 插件: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
###   - 点击每个请求上方的 "Send Request" 按钮
###
### 方式二：Swagger UI（网页）
###   - 打开 http://localhost:3002/api-docs
###   - 先调 POST /api/auth/login → 复制 accessToken
###   - 点右上角 "Authorize" → 输入 "Bearer <token>" → Authorize
###   - ✅ 之后刷新页面 token 也会保留，无需重复输入
###   - ⚠️ accessToken 有效期 15 分钟，过期需重新登录获取
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002/api
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbXFnMXA2amQwMDAwc3Bwbm43dGxzZGpqIiwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0MUBleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTU3ODI2NCwiZXhwIjoxNzgyMTgzMDY0fQ.9weVIHjo6hxlmE2zwXNjcAli1rLPy7w29r5OrHVmmPM
@userId = <从登录返回的 user.id 复制到这里>
@planId = <从创建规划返回的 id 复制到这里>
@resumeId = <先调 3.1 上传简历 → 从返回的 data.id 复制到这里>

### ===========================================
# 1. 健康检查
### ===========================================

GET http://localhost:3002
Content-Type: application/json

### ===========================================
# 2. 认证模块
### ===========================================

### 2.1 注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test1@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456",
  "name": "测试用户"
}

### 2.2 登录（保存返回的 accessToken）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123456"
}

### 2.3 刷新 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbXFnMG1qa3AwMDAwMWY3MDR5enZ5bDJuIiwiZW1haWwiOiJ1c2VyQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgxNTgwNDEwLCJleHAiOjE3ODIxODUyMTB9.mkRBJi_-uJpsYsFvLrkLFHRmgRe31Dy_MYJX8Jgmw4I"
}

### 2.4 获取用户信息（需登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.5 修改个人资料
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新名字",
  "education": "本科-计算机科学与技术",
  "targetPosition": "前端开发工程师"
}

### 2.6 获取全部用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.7 获取指定用户（传 id 查询参数）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?id={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
# 3. 简历模块
### ===========================================

### 3.1 上传简历
POST {{baseUrl}}/resumes/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-resume.pdf
------boundary--

### 3.2 简历列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/resumes?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 简历详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/resumes/{{resumeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.4 编辑简历
# 支持修改的字段（任选一个或多个）:
#   title              - 简历标题
#   parsedData         - 完整的解析数据对象（替换整块）
#   skills             - 技能标签数组
#   status             - 状态（parsing / completed / failed）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/resumes/{{resumeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "修改后的简历名称",
  "skills": ["Java", "Spring Boot", "MySQL", "Redis"],
  "parsedData": {
    "basicInfo": { "name": "张三", "phone": "13800138000" },
    "skills": ["Java", "Spring Boot"],
    "education": [
      { "school": "北京大学", "major": "计算机", "degree": "本科" }
    ],
    "experience": [],
    "projects": [],
    "summary": "3年Java开发经验"
  }
}

# 如果只想补齐 skills 字段，可以只传:
# PUT {{baseUrl}}/resumes/{{resumeId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
# 
# {
#   "skills": ["Java", "Spring Boot", "MySQL"]
# }

### 3.5 删除简历
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/resumes/{{resumeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
# 4. AI 模块
### ===========================================

### 4.1 简历解析（需要先配置 LLM API Key）
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/resume/parse
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "姓名：张三\n电话：13800138000\n邮箱：zhangsan@example.com\n\n教育经历：\n北京大学 - 计算机科学与技术 - 本科 - 2018.09 - 2022.06\n\n工作经历：\n字节跳动 - 前端开发工程师 - 2022.07 - 至今\n负责公司核心业务的前端架构设计与开发\n\n技能：\nJavaScript, TypeScript, React, Vue.js, Node.js"
}

### 4.2 生成面试题
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/interview/question
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": "前端开发工程师",
  "difficulty": "mid",
  "count": 3,
  "skills": ["React", "TypeScript", "Vue"],
  "industry": "互联网"
}

### 4.3 评估回答
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/interview/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请解释 React 中 useState 和 useReducer 的区别以及各自的适用场景",
  "answer": "useState 适用于简单的状态管理，比如布尔值、字符串等单一值。useReducer 适用于复杂的状态逻辑，比如包含多个子值的对象状态，或者下一个状态依赖于前一个状态的场景。useReducer 还可以配合 Context 实现全局状态管理。",
  "expectedAnswer": "useState 适合单一、简单的状态值；useReducer 适合复杂状态逻辑、多个关联状态、或需要重用状态更新逻辑的场景",
  "position": "前端开发工程师",
  "difficulty": "mid"
}

### 4.4 生成面试报告
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/interview/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "question": "请介绍你的项目经验",
      "answer": "我参与过电商平台的前端开发，使用 React+TypeScript 实现",
      "score": 75
    },
    {
      "question": "React 虚拟 DOM 的原理是什么",
      "answer": "虚拟 DOM 是真实 DOM 的 JS 对象表示，通过 diff 算法比较差异，批量更新真实 DOM",
      "score": 80
    }
  ]
}

### 4.5 生成职业规划
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/career/plan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentSkills": ["JavaScript", "HTML", "CSS", "Vue"],
  "targetPosition": "高级前端开发工程师",
  "experience": "1年前端开发经验",
  "education": "本科-计算机科学与技术",
  "goals": "希望在2年内成长为高级前端工程师"
}

### ===========================================
# 5. 面试模块
### ===========================================

### 5.1 创建面试
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetPosition": "前端开发工程师",
  "difficulty": "mid",
  "resumeId": 1
}

### 5.2 面试列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.3 面试详情
@interviewId = 你的面试ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/{{interviewId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.4 面试对话记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/{{interviewId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.5 提交回答
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews/{{interviewId}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "闭包是指有权访问另一个函数作用域中变量的函数，常用于数据私有化和函数工厂"
}

### 5.6 手动结束面试
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews/{{interviewId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.7 生成面试反馈（需先完成面试）
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews/{{interviewId}}/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
# 6. 职业规划
### ===========================================

### 6.1 创建职业规划（AI 生成差距分析 + 学习路线 + 市场洞察）
POST {{baseUrl}}/career/plan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentSkills": ["JavaScript", "HTML", "CSS", "Vue", "Git"],
  "targetPosition": "全栈开发工程师"
}

### 6.2 职业规划列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/career/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.3 规划详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/career/plans/{{planId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.4 市场洞察数据
GET {{baseUrl}}/career/market-insight?position=全栈开发工程师
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
# 7. WebSocket 实时面试（T-012）
# 
# ⚠️ REST Client 不支持 WebSocket 测试！
# 请使用以下方法之一：
# 
# 方法一：浏览器控制台
#   1. 打开 F12 开发者工具 → Console
#   2. 粘贴以下代码：
#   
#   const ws = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:3002/ws/interview?token={{token}}');
#   ws.onmessage = (e) => console.log('收到:', JSON.parse(e.data));
#   ws.onopen = () => {
#     console.log('已连接');
#     ws.send(JSON.stringify({
#       interviewId: '你的面试ID',
#       content: '闭包是指有权访问另一个函数作用域中变量的函数'
#     }));
#   };
# 
# 方法二：安装 wscat 工具
#   npm install -g wscat
#   wscat -c "ws://localhost:3002/ws/interview?token={{token}}"
#   连接后输入 JSON 消息：
#   {"interviewId":"你的面试ID","content":"你的回答"}
# 
# 方法三：使用 WebSocket 测试网站
#   访问 https://www.websocket.org/echo.html
#   URL: ws://localhost:3002/ws/interview?token={{token}}
# ===========================================
### WebSocket 面试消息协议

### 7.1 客户端 → 服务端 (user_answer)
# {
#   "interviewId": "xxx",
#   "content": "你的回答内容"
# }

### 7.2 服务端 → 客户端 (ai_message_chunk)
# {
#   "messageId": "uuid",
#   "chunk": "流式片段文本"
# }

### 7.3 服务端 → 客户端 (ai_message_done)
# {
#   "messageId": "uuid",
#   "fullContent": "完整回复",
#   "feedback": "评语",
#   "score": 85,
#   "strengths": ["优点1"],
#   "weaknesses": ["不足1"],
#   "isFollowUp": false,
#   "nextAction": "nextQuestion",
#   "nextQuestion": "下一题...",
#   "followUpContent": null
# }

### 7.4 服务端 → 客户端 (error)
# {
#   "code": 401,
#   "message": "未提供认证令牌"
# }
